n_15854_translations":{"at":1772689475155,"data":{"id":15854,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Frank Theodore 'Ted' Levine (born May 29, 1957) is an American actor. He is best known for his roles as Buffalo Bill in The Silence of the Lambs and Captain Leland Stottlemeyer in the television series Monk.","name":"Ted Levine","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Fils de Milton Dmitri Levine et Charlotte Virginia (née Clark), tous deux docteurs en médecine et membres de l'association Physicians for Social Responsibility, Ted est d'origine russo-juive par son père et canadienne par sa mère. Son enfance se déroule à Oak Park dans l'Illinois. En 1975, il devient étudiant du collège de Marlboro, l'établissement affilié à l'université d'arts libéraux. À l'âge de 25 ans, il joue le rôle de Stubbs dans l'adaptation de Moby Dick au Théâtre Remains à Chicago. Le spectacle recevra le prix des Jeff Awards de la meilleure production théâtrale de 19821.\n\nIl a joué dans une multitude d'autres registres : handicapé mental dans Bullet, chasseur de primes dans Cavale sans issue, général de l'armée dans Evolution et Wild Wild West, policier dans Heat et Fast and Furious, directeur d'asile psychiatrique dans Shutter Island…","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Ted Levine (* 29. Mai 1957 in Bellaire, Belmont County, Ohio, eig. Frank Theodore Levine) ist ein US-amerikanischer Film- und Fernsehschauspieler, der vorwiegend als Nebendarsteller in Filmen und Serien mitwirkt. Im deutschen Sprachraum ist er vor allem durch seine Rolle als Captain Leland Stottlemeyer in der Fernsehserie Monk bekannt sowie als Serienmörder Buffalo Bill in Das Schweigen der Lämmer.\n\nEr spielte Anfang der 1980er Jahre zunächst an Theatern in Vermont, Michigan und Chicago, wo er an der Universität den Master of Fine Arts erhielt. Mittlerweile arbeitet er hauptsächlich für Film und Fernsehen. In den 1980er Jahren wirkte er unter anderem in der Serie Crime Story mit. Weltweite Aufmerksamkeit erreichte er aber erst 1991 als Serienkiller Jame 'Buffalo Bill' Gumb in dem Thriller Das Schweigen der Lämmer. Levine wollte nicht auf die Rolle eines Psychopathen festgelegt werden und spielte in der Folgezeit weniger abgründige Charaktere: Militärs, Polizisten oder Familienväter. 1998 trat er zusammen mit Patrick Stewart in der zweiteiligen Fernsehadaption von Melvilles Moby Dick auf. Von 2002 bis 2009 übernahm er an der Seite von Tony Shalhoub in der Serie Monk die Rolle des Captain Leland Stottlemeyer.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"Фрэнк Теодор «Тед» Левин (родился 29 мая 1957 года) - американский актер. Он известен своими ролями в качестве Буффало Билла в «Молчание ягнят» и капитан Лиланда Стоттлеймайера в телесериале «Монк».","name":"Тед Левайн","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"테드 러바인","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"泰德·李凡","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"泰德·拉文是一名美国影视演员，1957年5月29日出生于俄亥俄州，贝莱尔Bellaire，Ohio，代表作有电影《沉默的羔羊》、电视剧《神探阿蒙》等，2008年获得演员工会奖。","name":"泰德·拉文","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Тед Левін","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"טד לווין","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"泰德·拉文是一名美國影視演員，1957 年 5 月 29 日出生於俄亥俄州，貝萊爾 Bellaire，Ohio，代表作有電影《沉默的羔羊》、電視劇《神探阿蒙》等，2008 年獲得演員工會獎。","name":"泰德·拉文","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"テッド・レヴィン","primary":false}}]}},"person_4556632_translations":{"at":1772689476445,"data":{"id":4556632,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Yao Jingyuan","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"姚景元","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"姚景元","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"姚景元","primary":false}}]}},"person_6000676_translations":{"at":1772691614911,"data":{"id":6000676,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"박재현","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Park Jae-hyeon","primary":false}}]}},"person_1906728_translations":{"at":1772691618200,"data":{"id":1906728,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Lauren Call","primary":true}}]}},"person_1019176_translations":{"at":1772691624079,"data":{"id":1019176,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Jaime Francisco García Fábregas is a Filipino actor and composer. Fábregas began his acting career in theatre before entering show business. He became a part of Repertory Philippines where he acted in many plays and musicals. He is a five-time Gawad Urian and two-time FAMAS winner.","name":"Jaime Fabregas","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PH","iso_639_1":"tl","name":"","english_name":"Tagalog","data":{"biography":"","name":"Jaime Fabregas","primary":true}}]}},"person_3830287_translations":{"at":1772691625347,"data":{"id":3830287,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"国义骞，男，演员，1984年7月1日出生。","name":"国义骞","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Guo Yiqian","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"國義騫","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"國義騫，男，演員，1984 年 7 月 1 日出生。","name":"國義騫","primary":false}}]}},"tv_309963_keywords":{"at":1772691627456,"data":{"id":309963,"results":[]}},"person_2692435_translations":{"at":1772691637606,"data":{"id":2692435,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Isaac Yang","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Isaac Yang","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"楊懿軒","primary":false}}]}},"person_5224569_translations":{"at":1772691648316,"data":{"id":5224569,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Mika Arias","primary":true}}]}},"person_578838_translations":{"at":1772691648866,"data":{"id":578838,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Shin Jung-keun","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"申正根 ，1966年9月26日出生于首尔，韩国舞台剧、影视演员。","name":"申正根","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"신정근","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"申正根","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"申正根 ，1966 年 9 月 26 日出生於首爾，韓國舞台劇、影視演員。","name":"申正根","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SK","iso_639_1":"sk","name":"Slovenčina","english_name":"Slovak","data":{"biography":"","name":"Shin Jung-keun","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Син Чон Гын","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Сін Чонґ Кин","primary":false}}]}},"person_1246802_translations":{"at":1772691661382,"data":{"id":1246802,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Jacob Lumet Cannavale (born May 1, 1995) is an American actor and musician. He appeared on Broadway in 2015 in the comedy Fish in the Dark by Larry David. He has also appeared on television's Nurse Jackie and The Mandalorian. He is the son of actor Bobby Cannavale and screenwriter Jenny Lumet, a grandson of film director Sidney Lumet, and a great-grandson of singer/actress Lena Horne.","name":"Jake Cannavale","primary":true}}]}},"person_1169789_translations":{"at":1772691670979,"data":{"id":1169789,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Michael Tao Dai Yu is a Hong Kong television actor.\n\nTao entered the acting industry in the 1980s, affiliating with TVB. It was during this period that Tao earned the name \"Housewife Killer\" due to his overwhelming popularity amongst housewives (who arguably constitute a majority of television viewing audiences in Hong Kong), solidifying his position as a first tier television actor in TVB.\n\nTao later moved over to rival ATV in 1997 after problems over his contract with TVB. His ATV series Flaming Brothers defeated the TVB rival show at the time, a landmark for ATV. Apart from filming ATV series, Tao has also filmed in China and Singapore. He returned to TVB in 2004 and has starred in a number of television series since. Once again, problems with his contract resulted in Tao leaving TVB in 2009 and worked mostly in mainland China and occasionally in Hong Kong.\n\nIn 2021, Tao gained popularity after numerous videos of him singing Andy Lau's 1996 song \"Reverse The Earth\" in a unique voice and style resurfaced. Tao was known to have performed at various Chinese malls singing various Cantonese/Mandarin pop songs for commercial events since 2020, and was imitated across the internet by various netizens, including Douyin, YouTube and Poki Ng from the Hong Kong boyband ERROR. This has also led to creation of fan groups on Facebook humorously advocating for Tao to become a full-fledged singer. Tao has responded positively, saying he enjoys entertaining people and jokingly hopes being able to catch up after Louis Koo's spot as favourite male singer in Hong Kong's Ultimate Song Chart Awards Presentation.","name":"Michael Tao Tai-Yu","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"陶大宇（Michael Tao），1963年8月26日出生于中国香港，毕业于无线电视艺员训练班，中国香港男演员。\n\n1983年，参演首部电视剧《北斗双雄》，1992年，在电视剧《壹号皇庭》系列中饰演江承宇；1995年，在刑侦剧《刑事侦缉档案》中饰演第一男主角张大勇，该剧以平均32点最高38点成为TVB全年收视冠军]，凭借《刑事侦缉档案》获得壹电视大奖十大艺人第一位。1996年，凭借《刑事侦缉档案2》蝉联壹电视大奖十大艺人第一位。1997年，转投香港亚视；1999年，主演电视剧《纵横四海》 。2003年重返无线，2005年，与郭可盈主演电视剧《心花放》]。2009年离开TVB赴中国内地发展。\n\n2013年12月，陶大宇获邀赴中国上海担任《第11届华鼎奖全球音乐满意度调查发布盛典》颁奖嘉宾 。2016年9月，主演的电视剧《隐世者们》播出。","name":"陶大宇","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"陶大宇（Michael Tao），1963 年 8 月 26 日出生於香港，畢業於無線電視藝員訓練班，香港男演員。\n\n1983 年，參演首部電視劇《北鬥雙雄》，1992 年，在電視劇《壹號皇庭》系列中飾演江承宇；1995 年，在刑偵劇《刑事偵緝檔案》中飾演第一男主角張大勇，該劇以平均 32 點最高 38 點成為 TVB 全年收視冠軍]，憑藉《刑事偵緝檔案》獲得壹電視大獎十大藝人第一位。1996 年，憑藉《刑事偵緝檔案 2》蟬聯壹電視大獎十大藝人第一位。1997 年，轉投香港亞視；1999 年，主演電視劇《縱橫四海》 。2003 年重返無線，2005 年，與郭可盈主演電視劇《心花放》]。2009 年離開 TVB 赴中國內地發展。\n\n2013 年 12 月，陶大宇獲邀赴中國上海擔任《第 11 屆華鼎獎全球音樂滿意度調查發佈盛典》頒獎嘉賓 。2016 年 9 月，主演的電視劇《隱世者們》播出。","name":"陶大宇","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Đào Đại Vũ","primary":false}}]}}}}